**TechNova Solutions – Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)**

**Q1: How many leaves are allowed per year?**
A: Employees are entitled to 20 annual leaves, 10 sick leaves, and 5 casual leaves per year.

**Q2: What are the working hours?**
A: Working hours are from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM, Monday to Friday.

**Q3: Can I take leave without approval?**
A: No, all leaves must be approved by your reporting manager in advance.

**Q4: What happens if I take unapproved leave?**
A: It will be treated as unpaid leave and may result in salary deduction.

**Q5: Is medical proof required for sick leave?**
A: Yes, if the sick leave exceeds 2 consecutive days.

**Q6: Can I use company laptop for personal work?**
A: No, company resources must be used only for official purposes.

**Q7: What should I do in case of emergency leave?**
A: Inform your manager as soon as possible.

